{"tid":1961132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Monkey won]新加坡推51億經濟援助方案　年滿21歲可提早本月獲3250港元","createTime":"2020-04-06T14:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T01:40:09.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f644e43d5467c5d10dfacb496e23a6691754f842","tid":1961132,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T14:38:35.000Z","msg":"新加坡今日（6日）推出第三套因應新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫症的援助方案，涉及51億坡元（約276億港元），包括年滿21歲的新加坡人可在本月提早獲得600坡元（約3250港元）現金補助。這是新加坡政府兩個月內因應疫情提出的第三個經濟援助方案。<br />\n<br />\n51億坡元資助中，有40億元會協助企業與員工，另外11億元給予家庭與個人。政府今年2月宣布向每名成年人派錢100至300坡元，3月時加碼至300至900坡元，8至9月發放。在最新公布中，政府加快派錢，稱首兩輪其中300元會連同另外多300元的補貼提早在本月發放。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200406/s00005/1586178273169/%e6%96%b0%e5%8a%a0%e5%9d%a1%e6%8e%a851%e5%84%84%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f%e6%8f%b4%e5%8a%a9%e6%96%b9%e6%a1%88-%e5%b9%b4%e6%bb%bf21%e6%ad%b2%e5%8f%af%e6%8f%90%e6%97%a9%e6%9c%ac%e6%9c%88%e7%8d%b23250%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200406%2Fs00005%2F1586178273169%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%258a%25a0%25e5%259d%25a1%25e6%258e%25a851%25e5%2584%2584%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%25e6%258f%25b4%25e5%258a%25a9%25e6%2596%25b9%25e6%25a1%2588-%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e6%25bb%25bf21%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%258f%25af%25e6%258f%2590%25e6%2597%25a9%25e6%259c%25ac%25e6%259c%2588%25e7%258d%25b23250%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%2585%2583&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lexphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=945c5ccc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200406%2Fs00005%2F1586178273169%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%258a%25a0%25e5%259d%25a1%25e6%258e%25a851%25e5%2584%2584%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%25e6%258f%25b4%25e5%258a%25a9%25e6%2596%25b9%25e6%25a1%2588-%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e6%25bb%25bf21%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%258f%25af%25e6%258f%2590%25e6%2597%25a9%25e6%259c%25ac%25e6%259c%2588%25e7